I’m heartbroken and speechless. I don’t see the point of living in a world where millions of people have to protest just to raise awareness about genocide! Where the powerful bunch close their eyes and ears, and continue to spread and support lies. 

What happened in Israel was wrong! I don’t know a single person who wasn’t heartbroken by the news. 

But to eliminate a whole nation and to punish them for crimes of a te**orist organization is inhumane and disgusting! It is NOT acceptable. We shouldn’t have to scream on top of our lungs to tell our leaders that killing innocent children and people is WRONG! 

If I can’t sleep at night and can’t stop crying over everything that’s going on in the world right now, I can’t even imagine how the people of Gaza are possibly dealing with these atrocities! Please pray for them, donate, attend rallies, and do whatever you can to support them. 💔

This is NOT about religion! This is about saving humanity!

Wake the fu*k up and consider humanity for a second! 

If you’re not talking about what’s going on in the Middle East (especially G*za) and the world at large, I urge you to consider why other people’s suffering doesn’t impact you. This is not about religion or politics! This is about humanity!
